Contributing
------------

1. Clone this repository (``git clone ...``)
2. Create virtualenv
3. Install package dependencies: ``pip install --upgrade -r requirements.txt``
4. Change some code
5. Run tests: in project root simply execute ``pytest``
6. Submit PR :)

